类 RichFlatMapFunction<IN,OUT>

  • 类型参数:
    IN - Type of the input elements.
    OUT - Type of the returned elements.
    所有已实现的接口:

    @Public
public abstract class RichFlatMapFunction<IN,OUT>
extends AbstractRichFunction
implements FlatMapFunction<IN,OUT>
    Rich variant of the FlatMapFunction. As a RichFunction, it gives access to the RuntimeContext and provides setup and teardown methods: RichFunction.open(org.apache.flink.configuration.Configuration) and RichFunction.close().

      • flatMap

        public abstract void flatMap(IN value,
                             Collector<OUT> out)
                      throws Exception
        从接口复制的说明: FlatMapFunction
        The core method of the FlatMapFunction. Takes an element from the input data set and transforms it into zero, one, or more elements.
        指定者:
        flatMap 在接口中 FlatMapFunction<IN,OUT>
        参数:
        value - The input value.
        out - The collector for returning result values.
        抛出:
        Exception - This method may throw exceptions. Throwing an exception will cause the operation to fail and may trigger recovery.
